{"tid":1346234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新鴻基: 對事件表示震驚 一直未能聯絡上警方","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:15:27.000Z","uid":87069,"like":10,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5c1fc6cedc9ae1e07b80467cffba37dec03fbc87","tid":1346234,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"【即時】(08:47) 昨日白衫人襲擊市民的地點之一Yoho Mall發表聲明，對事件表示震驚，又指昨日一直未能聯絡警方，全文如下：<br />\n<br />\nYoho Mall服務處對於7月21日晚上有市民在港鐵元朗站通往商場的通道上遇到襲擊及受傷，深表震驚和遺憾，並向受傷市民致以慰問，希望他們早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/354639/元朗黑夜-yoho-mall聲明-有市民遇襲-職員無法聯絡警方\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F354639%2F%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-yoho-mall%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%9C%89%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E9%81%87%E8%A5%B2-%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E8%81%AF%E7%B5%A1%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=51671e1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/354639/元朗黑夜-yoho-mall聲明-有市民遇襲-職員無法聯絡警方</a><br />\n<br />\n算吧啦新地，經過尋晚無人會敢買Yoho town咋樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4562aa879b4ebbdf2632fa2be03f562154df2c3","tid":1346234,"uid":34275,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:48:31.000Z","msg":"Shk=Sell Hong Kong"},{"pid":"32abbd8df5cc4f847ad6247171f3cee55768fcbf","tid":1346234,"uid":250443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 寫咗個白宮聯署<br />\nrequest國際人道救援/援助<br />\n已經有二萬三千人簽咗<br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同幫手推推post thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hk